06:57.960 --> 07:03.240
Jamila Jamil, an actress known for the NBC show The Good Place, has now started a campaign

07:03.240 --> 07:05.640
called I-Way.

07:05.640 --> 07:09.800
The purpose of her campaign is to call out and show celebrities and point out to regular

07:09.800 --> 07:13.880
people that celebrities and influencers have amazing resources to some of the best food,

07:13.880 --> 07:18.680
the best personal trainers, the best gyms, and the best magazine editors in the world.

07:18.680 --> 07:22.080
So no wonder they look better than the average person.

07:22.080 --> 07:26.560
